query:
INSERT INTO organization_members (organization_id, user_id, created_at, updated_at)
SELECT o.id, u.id, NOW(), NOW()
FROM organizations o
INNER JOIN users u ON u.id = o.owner_id
WHERE u.email = 'wyatt@gtmplanetary.com'
LIMIT 1
